                           'Accumulus' 1.0

                         by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" Accumulus " link play} is a Workbench game where you click on various types
of tiles, and as tiles are clicked on, they disappear and tiles
above them fall down in the vacated spaces. The goal is to get
tiles to fall so no tiles of the same type are placed next to
each other.

  Have fun!

